{"tid":1595642,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Jackson王嘉爾竟然唔識內地潮語　不滿吐槽：就這麼討厭打字嗎？","createTime":"2019-09-26T07:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T00:48:04.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":166,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"6b0e254b9fbf8c31fdb84bef37f6e3acab246837","tid":1595642,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3331715/org/537e860e5c8f08a6b9267764da56005e.jpg/w2z0u-ZR1O-bi-3KAEIBrowtfRknFy19_08MZv9PDGY?v=w960r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3331715%2Forg%2F537e860e5c8f08a6b9267764da56005e.jpg%2Fw2z0u-ZR1O-bi-3KAEIBrowtfRknFy19_08MZv9PDGY%3Fv%3Dw960r16_9&h=cec72ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGOT7中的香港成員Jackson王嘉爾在中國發展得非常好，自個人工作室TEAM WANG成立後，在內地的演藝事業可說是更上一層樓。不過早前在節目《音浪合伙人》中自稱是「中國90後」的他，面對內地的網絡用語竟幾乎一竅不通，更逼使到王嘉爾要開聲吐槽一番。<br />\n<br />\n明天（26日）將發行首張數碼專輯《MIRRORS》的王嘉爾，日前率先公開單曲《Bullet to the heart》的MV，反應相當熱烈。趕緊宣傳新碟的Jackson早前亦接受了傳媒《部嘮娛》的訪問，當中測試他對內地網絡用語認知度的部分最近意外登上微博熱搜榜。訪問中記者向王嘉爾提供了8個網絡及追星潮語，包括「nbcs」、「dbq」和「plgg」等，可是他卻只猜中其中一個。<br />\n<br />\n王嘉爾面對內地的網絡用語竟幾乎一竅不通？（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n王嘉爾邊等記者開估時，他亦忍不住當場在鏡頭前吐槽：「就這麼討厭打字嗎？以後所有的文字，你寫的論文都是用這個縮寫，你問那個教授看不看得懂。」心急和委屈的模樣令粉絲哭笑不得。有粉絲笑言Jackson自稱是「中國90後」卻不懂時下年輕人的潮語，同時亦有粉絲表示同意偶像的吐糟，指自己也跟不上現今大量湧現的網絡用語。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3331151/org/50c9aee94a3a238b27157dff3daff6b9.jpg/tDEQaMIKF2IHyNVSk3ZGlpIKWzgisZqP5FUCb-RVAm8?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3331151%2Forg%2F50c9aee94a3a238b27157dff3daff6b9.jpg%2FtDEQaMIKF2IHyNVSk3ZGlpIKWzgisZqP5FUCb-RVAm8%3Fv%3Dw960&h=5a4d940e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJackson的首張數碼專輯將於明天發行。（IG/@jacksonwang852g7）<br />\n<br />\n除了訪問中出現過的內地網絡用語外，小編嚴選了幾個測試一下讀者！<br />\n<br />\n1. nbcs<br />\n2. nssd<br />\n3. dbq<br />\n4. drl<br />\n5. xyxf<br />\n6. xjm<br />\n7. plgg<br />\n8. SMMY<br />\n9. xswl<br />\n10. bhys<br />\n11. xxj<br />\n12. BT<br />\n<br />\n按圖開估睇答案："},{"pid":"b71d556810a2c742b115248c7a10085abd3e7abc","tid":1595642,"uid":22839,"like":109,"dislike":0,"score":109,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:08:48.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩屌你老母"},{"pid":"075c0f1a3644250e7ab7593a0bb8d777f0459eb9","tid":1595642,"uid":62011,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"DLLM"},{"pid":"95c08f06619490b404659f31b17820844b12d5e5","tid":1595642,"uid":138138,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:09:38.000Z","msg":"bt都要估？ 成日用嫁喎"},{"pid":"d17a60fe7595af981f19838fe8ee870bf8d0b20d","tid":1595642,"uid":122940,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:09:48.000Z","msg":"呢條友成日乸型咁"},{"pid":"8b0d3e2770cf8da53d51c29327b777fb452ad776","tid":1595642,"uid":67302,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:10:02.000Z","msg":"文盲國家嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪撚講啦"},{"pid":"eddc3bc3bf1da19f38fbf264804b638f33c1cf80","tid":1595642,"uid":24730,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:10:24.000Z","msg":"Cls"},{"pid":"933d8e2f7b5fa46cba1efd843b0e97ae7f9a91ab","tid":1595642,"uid":120772,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:10:48.000Z","msg":"岩嫁喇 大陸人阿 簡體阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755e087a2267d2bd83dceab785c282657ab06a42","tid":1595642,"uid":40460,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:10:53.000Z","msg":"dllm cls<br />\n大陸新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889e9f20335e8974faeb8c8bbc8493f3863515f8","tid":1595642,"uid":251333,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:11:12.000Z","msg":"做咩樣衰左咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd4f0c32f6381799105ff07a4928e212e9286ed","tid":1595642,"uid":76632,"like":10,"dislike":0,